
1Changing the port for a single project on a single run
run-app -Dserver.port=9090 

2.Changing the port for a single project permanently
(Buildconfig)
grails.project.work.dir = "target/work"
grails.project.target.level = 1.6
grails.project.source.level = 1.6
grails.server.port.http = 9091

3.Changing the port for all Grails projects permanently
Shell
(settings.groovy)
grails.server.port.http = 9092



cp -a /source/. /dest/

